title: Narrative

* This example shows a simple table of contents using the ''parentField'' and ''level'' parameter

* The "root" element is `parent: Contents`

* The macro-call uses the ''parentField'' to define a tree structure

* The ''level'' parameter limits the displayed depth to ''2 levels''

** `hh-hh-hh` at level 3 should ''not'' be visible

{{examples-overview}}

